WEBVTT

00:06:58.667 --> 00:07:02.643
shows the eight significant
health effects of climate change.

00:07:02.667 --> 00:07:05.351
H: Heat illnesses.

00:07:05.375 --> 00:07:09.601
E: Exacerbation of heart and lung disease.

00:07:09.625 --> 00:07:11.934
A: Asthma worsening.

00:07:11.958 --> 00:07:13.809
T: Traumatic injuries,

00:07:13.833 --> 00:07:16.434
especially during extreme weather events.

00:07:16.458 --> 00:07:19.726
W: Water and foodborne illnesses.

00:07:19.750 --> 00:07:21.976
A: Allergies worsening.

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:27.309
V: Vector-borne diseases spreading,
like Zika, dengue and Lyme.

00:07:27.333 --> 00:07:30.792
And E: Emotional stresses increasing.